Multiple app variant

--> problem ye hai ki aap ek sath alg alg type ka ek hi aap nhi chla skte means if u want to run preview ,developemnt ,production all type app in same device i,ye nhi ho skta ek device pe ek type ka hi chlega kyuki app-id sbka same hi rhta hai ,is problem ko solve krne ke liye hi multiple aap variant use hota hai

Solurion for android is application-id

convert app.json to app.config.ts

also after this step need to create build

