<!-- Over the top/air updates -->

1.npx expo install expo-updates 2. eas update:configure
it will add a feild called "channel":"developemnt" /"preview" / "production" in eas.json inside build,production,and preview

then again create build

then u can send updated by this command ---> eas update --channel preview --message "Fix login button alignment"

Assignment -> update on Demand by using expo-updates library ,like if new update is availabe then show a pop up in app that update is available if user click on update then update the app otherwise not
